{"tid":1304762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〔投票〕有關TVB及連儂牆之貼文","createTime":"2019-07-10T16:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T12:29:10.000Z","uid":200758,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a46995ba3d4e460a8c5611ee22f9058dc126805","tid":1304762,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:45:39.000Z","msg":"見到呢幾日講TVB同連儂牆嘅post太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重要嘅post例如五大訴求、黑警、監控燈柱、社會信用系統好容易沉晒底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為免令運動失焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我建議開個post集中討論TVB同連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩就係集中post度講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有人單獨開post講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好推 唔好正負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n贊成<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bgk8ooU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbgk8ooU.gif&h=57c62c67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反對<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QkmziXi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQkmziXi.gif&h=eefe6a53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"999028d27e219fd208fb36020e183a228e4fe1e0","tid":1304762,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa4ae0686c34536961df4e6398d9e9877881dd2c","tid":1304762,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63018690d5e483dc7e35c015517ece48995d5afe","tid":1304762,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T16:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" cla